### login Veterinarian
POST http://localhost:8080/loginJWT
content-type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "password": "password123"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));
    client.log("token: " + response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));
%}

### Create veterinarian
POST http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian
content-type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "firstName": "Cristina",
  "lastName": "de la Iglesia",
  "phoneNumber": "691384027",
  "email": "cristinadelaig2@gmail.com",
  "address": "c/Cala Pola nº2",
  "licenseNumber": 3,
  "yearsOfExperience": 10
}

