### Get available veterinarians
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/available
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get all veterinarians
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Create a walk-in visit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/1/visits/walk-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "petId": 1,
  "ownerId": 2,
  "agendaId": 3,
  "duration": 30,
  "reason": "Pupa",
  "price": 20
}
### Create a visit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "petId": 1,
  "ownerId": 2,
  "agendaId": 3,
  "id": null,
  "startDate": "2025-11-20T10:00:00",
  "duration": 15,
  "reason": "Getting spayed",
  "price": 1000
}

### Reeschedule visit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "petId": 1,
  "ownerId": 2,
  "agendaId": 3,
  "startDate": "2025-11-30T10:00:00",
  "duration": 0,
  "reason": null,
  "price": null
}

### Get all visits that occur in a period
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/1/visits/start/2024-01-01/end/2026-12-31
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
### Get all visits
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Modify status to not shown up
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/3/noshow
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
### Start a visit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1/initiate
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### End a visit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1/complete
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
### Get a visit by Id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get a visit by Id NOT FOUND
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/10
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Add diagnosis to visit
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1/diagnosis
content-type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}


{
  "diagnosis": "El perro tiene una fractura en la pata trasera derecha.",
  "notes": "Se recomienda reposo absoluto y analgésicos."
}
### Cancel a scheduled visit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/5/cancel
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Cancel a scheduled visit that is not in scheduled status error UNPROCESSABLE ENTITY
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/4/cancel
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Delete a visit
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Prescribe a medication
POST http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/6/prescribe-medication
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "quantityPrescribed": 1,
  "dosageInstructions": "ddd",
  "duration": 3,
  "visitID": 6,
  "medicationId": 1
}
### Checks if pet is incompatible with medicine
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/pet/1/incompatible/1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Prescribe a treatment in a visit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/visits/1/prescribe-treatment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

{
  "treatmentId": 1,
  "name": "Nail clipper",
  "description": "Cuts animals nails",
  "cost": 50
}

### Get a veterinarian's agenda
GET http://localhost:8080/api/veterinarian/1/agenda
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
